tasksel (2.76) unstable; urgency=low

  [ Kenshi Muto ]
  * japanese-desktop, korean-desktop, chinese-s-desktop, chinese-t-desktop:
    Add poppler-data which is non-free. poppler-data is needed for these
    languages to display PostScript or PDF on poppler applications, such
    as evince. Closes: #497000

