tasksel (2.64) unstable; urgency=low

  * Correct a bug that caused hidden enhancing tasks to be marked for install
    if they enhanced no available tasks. This is the problem that was
    underlying #406630.
  * Force epiphany into the gnome-desktop. It might not be pulled in via a
    dependency since other web browsers can satisfy the dependency.
    Closes: #370098
  * Also add epiphany-extensions.

 -- Joey Hess <joeyh@debian.org>  Tue, 16 Jan 2007 11:24:38 -0500

