    - desktop
    - czech-desktop
    - italian-desktop
    - slovak-desktop
  * Add firefox-locale-xx to:
    - desktop (the -en-gb and -en-us ones)
    - arabic-desktop
    - bulgarian-desktop
    - french-desktop
    - lithuanian-desktop
    - norwegian-desktop
    - punjabi-desktop
    - polish-desktop
    - romanian-desktop
    - slovak-desktop
    - swedish-desktop
    - turkish-desktop
    - chinese-s-desktop
    - chinese-t-desktop
