tasksel (2.26) unstable; urgency=low

  * Joey Hess
    - Remove doc-linux-zh-s, mozilla-locale-auto, debian-guide-es,
      debrecipes-es, doc-es-misc, linux-tutorial-es, and kde-i18n-th
      from tasks as none of those packages exist anymore. Anyone know of
      replacements?
    - Removed kbedic and cbedic from bulgarian since they are
      a) in contrib b) require manual downloads of data files so do not work
      out of the box so are not appropriate for a task anyway.
    - That's all the cruft in tasks. Closes: #260250
