      - Add Ukrainian translations (tasks/po/uk.po and po/uk.po)
      - Add "uk" to LANGS and LANGS_DESC in Makefile.
    - Ognyan Kulev
      - Initial Bulgarian translation (po/bg.po and tasks/po/bg.po)
      - Added "bg" to LANGS and LANGS_DESC in Makefile.
