  * Fixed some really stupid bugs
  * removed cvs build target from debian/rules (closes: #55621) [RC]
  * fixed -q option to properly queue package installs

 -- Randolph Chung <tausq@debian.org>  Wed, 19 Jan 2000 21:19:11 -0700

